Bug fixes and performance optimizations.

Full support for the iPhone 5 and 5th generation iPod touch. Bandwidth throttling: you can now control how much data you use on WiFi and cellular connections. Set your preferences in the Settings app. For some TV providers you no longer need to sign into your TV provider separately for WATCH Disney Channel WATCH Disney Junior and WATCH Disney XD. Sign into your TV provider in one app and you ll be automatically signed into your account in the other apps. We ve made some design improvements to the Home tab and player controls on the iPad We ve also fixed some minor bugs and made some memory optimizations to prevent crashes
